 ST_ProcessValues
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Live process data in ENGINEERING UNITS (Torr, degC, SLM).
 Populated by FB_FlowCalc / analog input scaling, consumed by FB_Hmi,
 FB_FaultMonitor and FB_PressureControl.
 pack_mode 1 so pyads structure_def offsets are byte-exact.
=============================================================================]]></Comment><BitSize>392</BitSize><SubItem><Name>rPt1Upstream</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PT-1 upstream pressure       (P1)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rPt2Downstream</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PT-2 downstream pressure     (P2)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>32</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rPt3AtmRef</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PT-3 atmospheric reference   (P3)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rDiffPressure</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PT-1 - PT-2 differential]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rTc1Spa</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TC1 SPA temperature]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rTc2FlowMeter</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TC2 flow meter temperature]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rTc3External</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TC3 external heater temperature]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rTc4Delivery</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TC4 delivery line temperature]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>224</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rFlowActual</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ F3 calculated steam flow     (V1472 filtered)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>256</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rFlowSetpoint</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ active flow setpoint         (V1550 SFR)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>288</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>rFlowRated</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ rated max flow               (V1552 RATED_FLOW)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>320</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bWaterFull</Name><Type>BOOL