 ST_Faults
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 One named BOOL per fault, replacing the legacy B1600.x / B1601.x / B1602.x
 bit-of-word addressing. Names taken from the element documentation table
 in the DS6 source. Legacy address noted per field for commissioning.
 pack_mode 1: each BOOL = 1 byte, so pyads can map this with a simple
 structure_def or read it as a byte array.
=============================================================================]]></Comment><BitSize>248</BitSize><SubItem><Name>bCabinetFlood</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Cabinet flood fault]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bPowerFault</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Power fault status]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>8</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bPneumaticHigh</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Pneumatic air pressure high]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>16</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bPneumaticLow</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Pneumatic air pressure low]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>24</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bUpstreamOverPress</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Upstream over pressure]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>32</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bDownstreamOverPress</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Downstream over pressure]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>40</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bRegUpcLow</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Regulate UPC low]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>48</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bRegUpcHigh</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Regulate UPC high]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>56</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bEcsaEquipment</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ ECSA equipment fault]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bFlowLow</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Flow low fault]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>72</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bFlowHigh</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Flow high fault]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>80</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bWaterEmpty</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Empty water level fault]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>88</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bWaterFill</Name><